<Author>pwelch
<Content>Some funny bus trouble This is really quite a nice hotel, its lobby is reasonable. The restaurant / breakfast area was very nice with a great buffet breakfast.For paying 69 EUR for a twin room for 2 nights, we were very pleased. You can buy wireless access.The bar was very swish, although expensive. We did not eat at the hotel, but chose the McDonalds just across the street.Our problem came with the airport bus, which never materialised late one evening, after just missing a bus we waited half an hour - but that bus never arrived, so we waited an hour altogether for a bus. The driver had clearly just been having a break, said something in broken English about taxis fighting and we were delayed longer waiting for a hotel employee to arrive. 
